# Getting Started with Next.js

Next.js 15 brings powerful features for building modern web applications. The App Router provides a new paradigm for routing and layouts.

## Key Features

- **Server Components** by default for better performance
- **Streaming** for faster perceived load times
- **Built-in SEO** with metadata APIs
- **TypeScript** support out of the box

## Learn More

Check out the [Next.js documentation](https://nextjs.org/docs) for in-depth guides.
